desc.en: MALL (EOS mall platform integration) MALL is a platform integral based on EOS issuance, totaling 100 million, never additional issuance, holding MALL to enjoy the platform quarterly profit dividend.
desc.zh: MALL (EOS mall platform integration) MALL是一个基于eos发行的电商平台积分，总量1亿，永不增发，持有MALL享受平台季度利润分红。
